title: Martin Molloy (1995) The Brown Album - Disc 1 (Pretty Brown)
description:
The Brown Album is the first compilation double-album of material taken from the Australian radio program Martin/Molloy, with comedians Tony Martin and Mick Molloy. Like each of the three Martin/Molloy albums, The Brown Album won the Best Comedy Release at the ARIA Music Awards, taking out the award in 1996
